Template: confluence/username
Type: string
Default: confluence
Description: Dedicated system account for the confluence:
 Confluence runs within a tomcat server and must use a dedicated account for 
 its operation so that the system's security is not compromised by running it 
 with superuser privileges.

Template: confluence/groupname
Type: string
Default: confluence
Description: Dedicated system group for confluence:
 Confluence runs within tomcat server and must use a dedicated group for its 
 operation so that the system's security is not compromised by running it with 
 superuser privileges.
